# Installation Instructions

## Installation with Cabal

You can install the `cflp` package using Cabal as follows.

1.  Unzip the sources and move into the source directory.

        > unzip cflp-*.zip
        > cd cflp-*

2.  Make the setup script executable and configure, build and install.

        > chmod +x Setup.lhs
        > ./Setup.lhs configure --user
        > ./Setup.lhs build
        > ./Setup.lhs install

